data.description: **OPEN HOUSE: Saturday Jan 20th 10:00am - 12:00 Noon**Darling Fully Updated Home in Easy West Valley Location. Quiet Neighborhood, Walking Distance to Elementary School, Neighborhood Parks and quick access to Main Roads. Charming Arched doorways welcome you home. NEW Paint throughout, New Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring, updated Trim & Windows. NEW Recessed Lighting added throughout. Darling Eat in Kitchen with Tile Floors, Picture Windows and Closet Pantry. 3/4 Bath off of Kitchen. Main Level has Primary Owners Bedroom complete with Custom Organizers in Closet and Attached En Suite Bathroom with NEW Updates. New Vanity, Tile in Shower and Water Closet. Original Built-ins for Storage in Hallway. Basement is Fully Finished with Dedicated Outside Entrance. 2 Additional Bedrooms and Storage room. Video Doorbell and Exterior Camera are Included.  Plenty of Parking on Driveway & Side Gravel Pad Leading to a 2 Car Detached Garage. Sprawling Fenced Backyard ready for a Green Thumb.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
